com.github.stefanbirkner.editors

Class EnumEditor<E extends Enum<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.stefanbirkner.editors.SfbPropertyEditorSupport<E>
      • com.github.stefanbirkner.editors.EnumEditor<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the enum to be edited.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyEditor

    public class EnumEditor<E extends Enum<E>>
extends SfbPropertyEditorSupport<E>
    This EnumEditor is a replacement for Java's built-in enum editor. Java's editor is only an internal class and therefore should not be used outside of Java. This class is expected to be used by you.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Stefan Birkner
